Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 看看那邊 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是模特兒還是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 森島學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部碰著我的…手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會那人就是她男友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能和那樣的美女交往 好羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 能和憧憬中的森島學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣地並肩走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月之前我連想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 我的臉上沾了些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和森島學姐這樣在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被你這樣一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我讓你變得更幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 橘你看看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候去見我的父母
