Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.35,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:07.18,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:11.87,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.60,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
