Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是橘他怎樣回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞得臉都泛紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概能想像到那時的情景了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現什麼有趣的報導了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座教堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺就是在這裡向奶奶求婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來遙的爺爺是英國人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候 他們常常對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往了還不到半年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺突然帶奶奶去教堂向她求婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是在奶奶畢業當天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 約好要永遠相愛下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在關係依然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得他們一臉幸福地向我談起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 經常和杰西卡說起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像爺爺奶奶那樣地結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個住在英國的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島·Sexy·杰西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比我大一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sexy…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡雖然去年就畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在畢業典禮那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被交往中的男友求婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到這事之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有那麼一點羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以約會時才和橘談起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚紗和見父母的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚的事是剛剛才想起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是他真這樣做了 我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這件事不要告訴橘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得好像我在求他做似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐 塚原學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎 坐在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和響聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘你才是 怎麼到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚熬夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有點累所以去保健室小睡了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 剛才遙說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:06:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙有個住在英國比她大一歲的親戚叫杰西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡她是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我大一歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子和我像極了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像森島學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的樣子換成金髮碧眼就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把學姐換成金髮碧眼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是預演啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這是誰都會經歷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也太直接了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新郎 橘純一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論新娘森島遙是疾病還是健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否願意毫無保留地愛她 尊重她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她忠誠直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我願意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘 森島遙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論新郎橘純一是疾病還是健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否願意毫無保留地愛他 尊重他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他忠誠直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我承認兩位結成夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來就是誓約的一吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經超出預演的範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 結婚儀式完了之後當然就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}新婚初夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊 純一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…前面那個重要的一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的確是要升學到醫學院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但專業不是婦產科而是兒科啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一樣不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要和小孩子打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次呢 是得知我懷孕了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次夫婦一起來看醫生的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 我們寶貝的情況怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經懷孕12週了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的努力沒白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面孕育著我們的新生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 是男孩還是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起結婚儀式和懷孕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後當然就是共享天倫之樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 不是都說好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天一天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從爸爸傍晚歸來時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響你也向爸爸說聲歡迎回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 歡迎回家的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然叫爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連親生父親都沒這樣叫過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯菜都準備好了 我們開飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是豪華套餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那媽媽也來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接叫我遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不直接叫我遙的話 我就不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你這樣子居然也能娶到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我還沒有問過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸向媽媽求婚時說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說嘛 那時說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 森島學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下次再繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繼續的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能需要先想好求婚的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼跑來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要早點見到遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你 我運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 剛剛才到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們真的是好像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙你沒怎麼變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的大小也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這兩位是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同級的塚原響 還有二年級的橘純一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好 響 還有純一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然森島學姐已經很有料了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是遙的男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和傳聞一樣長得很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 杰西卡你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 打個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也想想這裡是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎麼到日本來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來參觀遙的畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是來日本觀光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要特地過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你找到男朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會像奶奶和我那樣 在典禮上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲 有蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是到春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經走掉了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好加油啊 日本男兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對橘保密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說了的話 不就好像我在催他似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是直接讓男朋友這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多沒趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得在畢業前找到男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前頭 我可不是為了這個才開始交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上他的時間恰好是在畢業前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙也不是那種積極的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他知道那件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 還真的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐和杰西卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 老哥你快來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這期也很有趣 海狸三國志的最新一期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有個金髮碧眼的跟美也長得很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多少都不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看都沒看 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我不給你看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來參觀遙的畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐畢業後會升上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣見面的時間就會減少了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成那樣的話 真寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是橘啊 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 森島學姐沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業前夕 所以覺得寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也有可能是因為昨天中途就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 要繼續昨天的預演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 把塚原學姐也叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮一下 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐和平常不太一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 總覺得有些不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為要畢業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 無論是誰都會有感傷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 純一被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這份無法抑壓的感情發洩在打工上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正最近人手不太夠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說我沒被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你被森島學姐甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入茶道部 用好喝的茶治癒心靈創傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但純一你被森島學姐甩了的事已經傳遍學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又是薰幹的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年A班的橘純一 有你的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}請盡快到教職員辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有電話 純一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}2年A班的橘純一…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是橘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…杰西卡小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天剛認識就已經能聽出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話裡說Hello的人 我只認識你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理解得這麼快真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意打電話過來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將要離開輝日東一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去觀光期待已久的京都 很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要說的重點不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙她看起來很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在英國有很多喜歡遙的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有羅賓 泰利 史提亞還有淘氣的尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓遙覺得寂寞的話 遙可能就被他們搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油 橘純一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你好像不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我最喜歡學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會輸給英國的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅賓 泰利 史提亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有淘氣的尼爾 我都不會輸給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓學姐感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 從杰西卡那裡聽說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是孩提時代的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨這個你要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是橘的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時真的癢死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你親著我的膝蓋窩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人家叫你停 你也不肯停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但學姐的膝蓋窩很滑嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我還沒問過你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過 說不定這能弄懂小狗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再親一次的話應該就能弄懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那麼癢的才不要第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡充滿了回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直想在畢業前再來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這麼快就實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聲不吭地就拉著我走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間激動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 變回平時的學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森島學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:21:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要來我家玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:34.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}清晨傳來腳踏車的清脆鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:40.08,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}彷彿告訴著我時間逐漸流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:46.10,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這份無法消散的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:51.15,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定決心把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:23:03.13,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}點綴未來的預想於我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.62,0:23:09.51,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}暗自祈禱當中有你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:14.40,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:22.09,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:29.50,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:32.58,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:36.48,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次到橘家作客
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我招待學姐過來玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我要怎樣跟你父母打招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 父母外出工作不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也則在朋友家過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:23:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 你這個色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘純一 向你展示男子氣概
